loper.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/:where)) is alot like the `:is()` sudo-class but `:is()` works in sass and `:where()` doesn't\r\n\r\nthis\r\n```sass\r\n.my-class\r\n  :is(&)\r\n    color: red\r\n```\r\ncompiles to this\r\n```css\r\n:is(.my-class) {\r\n  color: red;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nand this\r\n```sass\r\n.my-class\r\n  :where(&)\r\n    color: red\r\n```\r\nshould compile to this (expected behavior)\r\n```css\r\n:where(.my-class) {\r\n  color: red;\r\n}\r\n```\r\nbut actually compiles to this (actual behavior)\r\n```css\r\n.my-class :where(&) {\r\n  color: red;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI am using sass 1.38.1 installed with npm","closed_by":{"login":"jathak","id":1817677,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4MTc2Nzc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1817677?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak","html_url":"https://github.com/jathak","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jathak/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sass/sass/issues/3130/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sass/sass/issues/3130/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}